{"tid":818263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Discovery Channel模擬強颱襲港片段 大廈玻璃爆破人心惶惶","createTime":"2018-09-14T03:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T03:59:30.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca2b7c36419ca04186e0ed7c1fa6528c51ba7f2","tid":818263,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180914/58679815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F58679815&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a3199665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F58679815&h=f248f85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180914/58679815</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年西北太平洋最強颱風「山竹」將吹襲香港，雖然預料山竹風力將減弱，但仍會在下周日以每小時200公里以上的風速襲港，風力達10級。不少人希望「山竹」可帶來風假，但現實中的強颱襲港是否只是多一個假？Discovery Channel 2006 年一個節目已經模擬超強颱風襲港的情景，片中高樓大廈玻璃爆破，消防員疲於奔命救人，到處受災害影響。<br />\nDiscovery Channel早於2006年播放一輯名為《Perfect Disaster》，故事設定在9月12日開始發現超強颱風的來臨，並在翌日直撲香港，片中大帽山風速高達每小時273公里，高樓大廈玻璃碎裂，沿岸地區海水倒灌，消防員爭取風眼接近香港的平靜時刻救人。"},{"pid":"6f9a8050d395543798c431afde00020e2defbd60","tid":818263,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"洗鬼佢模擬，求其一套災難片都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4898218575fb0604959f55964e2b581f139bf6af","tid":818263,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f9a8050d395543798c431afde00020e2defbd60","tid":818263,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"洗鬼佢模擬，求其一套災難片都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}